*PPD-Adobe: "4.3"
*%================================================================
*% Brother DCP-T230 - native macOS PPD (open-source reimplementation)
*%
*% Pairs with the `brother_dcpt230_pjl` Python CUPS filter.  The
*% filter accepts PWG Raster on stdin and emits PJL-wrapped PWG
*% Raster for USB delivery.  macOS handles all the work of turning
*% PDFs into PWG Raster via its built-in filter chain
*% (cgpdftoraster -> rastertopwg -> this filter -> USB backend).
*%
*% Protocol reverse-engineered from Brother's Linux binary
*% `brdcpt230filter`; see README.md for the analysis.
*%================================================================

*FormatVersion: "4.3"
*FileVersion:   "1.0"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*PCFileName: "BRT230.PPD"
*Manufacturer: "Brother"
*Product: "(DCP-T230)"
*ModelName: "Brother DCP-T230"
*ShortNickName: "DCP-T230"
*NickName: "Brother DCP-T230 (PWG/PJL native)"
*PSVersion: "(3010.000) 0"

*1284DeviceID: "MFG:Brother;MDL:DCP-T230;CMD:PJL,PWGRaster;"

*cupsVersion: 2.2
*cupsManualCopies: True
*cupsModelNumber: 0
*cupsLanguages: "en"
*cupsFilter: "image/pwg-raster 0 brother_dcpt230_pjl"

*% Raster format hints: tell cgpdftoraster / rastertopwg what to produce.
*% The DCP-T230 wants 8-bit-per-color sRGB (colorspace 19) for colour, or
*% 8-bit sGray (colorspace 18) for mono, at 300 DPI, uncompressed.
*cupsRasterVersion: "3"
*cupsBackSide: "Normal"

*LanguageLevel: "3"
*ColorDevice: True
*DefaultColorSpace: RGB
*FileSystem: False
*Throughput: "12"
*TTRasterizer: Type42
*VariablePaperSize: False
*DefaultResolution: 300dpi
*FreeVM: "1700000"

*% DCP-T230 is simplex-only with a single rear tray; no duplex or tray constraints needed.

*%==== Media Size =================================================
*OpenUI *PageSize/Media Size: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageSize
*DefaultPageSize: Letter
*PageSize Letter/US Letter:                      "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrLetter_B/US Letter (Borderless):     "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize Legal/US Legal:                        "<</PageSize[612 1008]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize Executive/Executive:                   "<</PageSize[522 756]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A4/A4:                                 "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrA4_B/A4 (Borderless):                "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A5/A5:                                 "<</PageSize[420 595]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A6/A6:                                 "<</PageSize[297 420]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrA6_B/A6 (Borderless):                "<</PageSize[297 420]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize B5/JIS B5:                             "<</PageSize[516 729]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize JISB6/JIS B6:                          "<</PageSize[363 516]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPostC4x6_S/4 x 6 in:                 "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPostC4x6_B/4 x 6 in (Borderless):    "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrIndexC5x8_S/5 x 8 in:                "<</PageSize[360 576]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrIndexC5x8_B/5 x 8 in (Borderless):   "<</PageSize[360 576]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPhotoL_S/3.5 x 5 in:                 "<</PageSize[252 360]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPhotoL_B/3.5 x 5 in (Borderless):    "<</PageSize[252 360]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPhoto2L_S/5 x 7 in:                  "<</PageSize[359 505]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize BrPhoto2L_B/5 x 7 in (Borderless):     "<</PageSize[359 505]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvDL/DL Envelope:                     "<</PageSize[312 624]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvC5/C5 Envelope:                     "<</PageSize[459 649]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize Env10/Com-10 Envelope:                 "<</PageSize[297 684]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize EnvMonarch/Monarch Envelope:           "<</PageSize[279 540]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize FanFoldGermanLegal/Folio:              "<</PageSize[612 936]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize 195x270mm/16K (195x270mm):             "<</PageSize[553 765]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize MexicanLegal/Mexico Legal:             "<</PageSize[612 963]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize IndianLegal/India Legal:               "<</PageSize[609 978]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageSize

*OpenUI *PageRegion/Media Size: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageRegion
*DefaultPageRegion: Letter
*PageRegion Letter/US Letter:                    "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrLetter_B/US Letter (Borderless):   "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion Legal/US Legal:                      "<</PageSize[612 1008]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion Executive/Executive:                 "<</PageSize[522 756]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A4/A4:                               "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrA4_B/A4 (Borderless):              "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A5/A5:                               "<</PageSize[420 595]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A6/A6:                               "<</PageSize[297 420]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrA6_B/A6 (Borderless):              "<</PageSize[297 420]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion B5/JIS B5:                           "<</PageSize[516 729]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion JISB6/JIS B6:                        "<</PageSize[363 516]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPostC4x6_S/4 x 6 in:               "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPostC4x6_B/4 x 6 in (Borderless):  "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrIndexC5x8_S/5 x 8 in:              "<</PageSize[360 576]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrIndexC5x8_B/5 x 8 in (Borderless): "<</PageSize[360 576]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPhotoL_S/3.5 x 5 in:               "<</PageSize[252 360]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPhotoL_B/3.5 x 5 in (Borderless):  "<</PageSize[252 360]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPhoto2L_S/5 x 7 in:                "<</PageSize[359 505]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion BrPhoto2L_B/5 x 7 in (Borderless):   "<</PageSize[359 505]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion EnvDL/DL Envelope:                   "<</PageSize[312 624]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion EnvC5/C5 Envelope:                   "<</PageSize[459 649]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion Env10/Com-10 Envelope:               "<</PageSize[297 684]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion EnvMonarch/Monarch Envelope:         "<</PageSize[279 540]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion FanFoldGermanLegal/Folio:            "<</PageSize[612 936]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion 195x270mm/16K (195x270mm):           "<</PageSize[553 765]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion MexicanLegal/Mexico Legal:           "<</PageSize[612 963]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion IndianLegal/India Legal:             "<</PageSize[609 978]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageRegion

