*%==== Paper Source ==============================================
*OpenUI *BRInputSlot/Paper Source: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 13 AnySetup *BRInputSlot
*DefaultBRInputSlot: AutoSelect
*BRInputSlot AutoSelect/Auto Select: ""
*BRInputSlot Manual/Manual Feed:     ""
*CloseUI: *BRInputSlot

*%==== Resolution & raster format =================================
*% Real raster resolution for cgpdftoraster / rastertopwg. We always
*% rasterise at 300 DPI and let the printer handle PJL PRINTQUALITY
*% separately (mirrors what Brother's Linux driver does).
*OpenUI *Resolution/Output Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 15 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 300dpi
*Resolution 300dpi/300 DPI: "<</HWResolution[300 300]/cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsBitsPerPixel 24/cupsColorSpace 19/cupsNumColors 3/cupsColorOrder 0/cupsCompression 0>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*%==== Print Quality ==============================================
*OpenUI *BRResolution/Print Quality: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 14 AnySetup *BRResolution
*DefaultBRResolution: Normal
*BRResolution Draft/Draft (fast):    ""
*BRResolution Normal/Normal:         ""
*BRResolution Fine/Fine (best):      ""
*CloseUI: *BRResolution

*%==== Colour / Mono ==============================================
*% Colour/mono also drives the raster format (sRGB vs sGray).
*OpenUI *BRMonoColor/Color / Mono: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 16 AnySetup *BRMonoColor
*DefaultBRMonoColor: FullColor
*BRMonoColor FullColor/Color:        "<</cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsBitsPerPixel 24/cupsColorSpace 19/cupsNumColors 3/cupsColorOrder 0>>setpagedevice"
*BRMonoColor Mono/Mono (Grayscale):  "<</cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsBitsPerPixel 8/cupsColorSpace 18/cupsNumColors 1/cupsColorOrder 0>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *BRMonoColor

*%==== Media Type =================================================
*OpenUI *BRMediaType/Media Type: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 17 AnySetup *BRMediaType
*DefaultBRMediaType: Plain
*BRMediaType Plain/Plain Paper:      ""
*BRMediaType Inkjet/Inkjet Paper:    ""
*BRMediaType Glossy/Glossy Paper:    ""
*BRMediaType Recycled/Recycled Paper: ""
*BRMediaType Env/Envelope:           ""
*BRMediaType EnvThin/Envelope (Thin): ""
*BRMediaType EnvThick/Envelope (Thick): ""
*CloseUI: *BRMediaType

*%==== Duplex (disabled — DCP-T230 is simplex-only) ===============
*OpenUI *Duplex/2-Sided Printing: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *Duplex
*DefaultDuplex: None
*Duplex None/Off: "<</Duplex false>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Duplex

*DefaultFont: Courier
*Font Courier: Standard "(002.004S)" Standard ROM
*Font Courier-Bold: Standard "(002.004S)" Standard ROM
*Font Courier-BoldOblique: Standard "(002.004S)" Standard ROM
*Font Courier-Oblique: Standard "(002.004S)" Standard ROM
*Font Helvetica: Standard "(001.006S)" Standard ROM
*Font Helvetica-Bold: Standard "(001.007S)" Standard ROM
*Font Helvetica-BoldOblique: Standard "(001.007S)" Standard ROM
*Font Helvetica-Oblique: Standard "(001.006S)" Standard ROM
*Font Times-Roman: Standard "(001.007S)" Standard ROM
*Font Times-Bold: Standard "(001.007S)" Standard ROM
*Font Times-Italic: Standard "(001.007S)" Standard ROM
*Font Times-BoldItalic: Standard "(001.009S)" Standard ROM
*Font Symbol: Special "(001.007S)" Special ROM
